{"tid":1902714,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［盲毛連登仔］法例寫明：預算開支總額須抱括在議案中，並一同提交立法會！","createTime":"2020-02-28T13:28:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T13:55:17.000Z","uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7df11a31be2086e981603f0a6b034f29e61b73cf","tid":1902714,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T13:28:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap2!zh-Hant-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap2%21zh-Hant-HK&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJDe9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=a64bf362\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap2!zh-Hant-HK</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNo0aF0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNo0aF0.png&h=d44d5f2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃毓民：警隊開支撥款是不能分拆！ 要求分拆都係唔識野！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902216\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902216</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個二個係到講碌撚個仔點樣<br />\n收左幾多共產黨錢 真係好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來真係法例已經寫到明係預算總目，者係無得拆開<br />\n<br />\n係立法會到質疑佢點解唔同警隊開支分拆根本反映身為議員連法例都唔清楚<br />\n條氣唔順咪去JR<br />\n政府跟法例做你話佢乜<br />\n一係就就拉冧佢，但又怕俾人屌搞到無一萬<br />\n一係就提修正減警隊開支<br />\n一係就推翻個政權"},{"pid":"c3b7842ce3ba44968f81be54cebf5e56d9e5bc26","tid":1902714,"uid":61914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T13:32:20.000Z","msg":"其實無興趣知佢講乜<br />\n樓主可唔可以唔好日日幫佢宣傳"},{"pid":"71429c257c61480e15ad5f3faca59cc89d0ce63a","tid":1902714,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3b7842ce3ba44968f81be54cebf5e56d9e5bc26","tid":1902714,"uid":61914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T13:32:20.000Z","msg":"其實無興趣知佢講乜<br />\n樓主可唔可以唔好日日幫佢宣傳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T13:36:08.000Z","msg":"證明你地只係